name: It's a Trap! - D&D 5E OGL theme
description: # It's A Trap! - 5th Edition OGL theme_v3.0 Updates_* The theme has been updated to be compatible with ItsATrap v3.0.This is a D&D 5th edition trap theme for the It's A Trap! script, compatible withthe 5th Edition (OGL by Roll20) character sheet.To use this theme for the It's A Trap! script, enter '5E-OGL' for the ```theme``` user option.
